facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, most-favoured-nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with most-favoured-nation status was 5.2 % in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with preferential status declined from 4.9 % in 2005 to 4.5% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, most-favored nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average most-favored nation status tariff applied by developed countries declined from 1.1 % in 2000 to 0.8% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average preferential status tariff applied by developed countries declined from 0.9 % in 2000 to 0.5% in 2018.
